---
title: Organic Beef Meatballs & Onion Gravy with Charred Peas & Mashed Potatoes
description: Calling all comfort food fans! Wait…who isn’t a fan?! This week’s selection ticks all of the feel-good boxes. Warmly spiced meatballs, à la Sweden, draped in rich and creamy onion sauce; check! Fluffy, sour cream mashed spuds and buttery, skillet charred peas; check, check! The only thing missing is your fave dining companion. And we won’t tell if you enjoy this meal in your PJs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6451277d1a9567b5c9030206-3a6d0465.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6542883baa83c24f3b0273ed.pdf
